  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In a longitudinal, prospective and observational study, patients with PCOS and controls wore
      the SenseWear Armband for 2 days. Resting metabolic rati (kcal/die), total energy expenditure
      (MET, kcal) were evaluated. Ultrasonographic pelvic examinations, hirsutism score,
      anthropometric and menstrual pattern evaluation, hormonal profile assays, oral glucose
      tolerance test (OGTT) and lipid profile were performed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
